<title type="html"><![CDATA[4/4(Sat.)Coronavirus: Air pollution and CO2 fall rapidly/'The phone slipped into the bath':(Host:Danny)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=378&amp;p=395#p395"><![CDATA[
4/4(Sat.)Coronavirus: Air pollution and CO2 fall rapidly as virus spreads/'The phone slipped into the bath': Conference call tales(Host:Danny)<br /><br />Article1:Coronavirus: Air pollution and CO2 fall rapidly as virus spreads<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-51944780">https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-51944780</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.That is a ' good' consequence of the catastrophe. Do you get any benefit from the pandemic?<br />2.Last year is an year European promoting the importance of environmental protection. What will happen after the pandemic? <br />3.Does the virus affect you? Please share your experiences or stories.<br /> <br />Article2:'The phone slipped into the bath': Conference call tales<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/business-52032849">https://www.bbc.com/news/business-52032849</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.Taiwan is a few countries which still allow students going to school. Do you prepare for online learning or working?<br />2. Are you and your classmate or colleague willing to study or work online?<br />3.What is the advantage or disadvantage of study or work from home.<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk<br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion<br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences<br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven,<br />板橋民生路二段237 號,<br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30,<br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Wed Apr 01, 2020 1:17 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
